## ▶️ How to Run

```bash
# 1. Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/krishrrathore/genz-social-media-eda
cd genz-social-media-eda

# 2. Install dependencies
pip install pandas numpy matplotlib seaborn jupyter

# 3. Place the dataset in the correct path, then run
jupyter notebook notebook.ipynb
```

